                     <interp inst="t18311020-98-person748" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was at the corner of Paternoster-row on Friday evening; I saw the prosecutor take the prisoner by the collar, and take the handkerchief from his breast-pocket, or his breast, and I went up and took him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18311020-98-person749">
                  THOMAS 
                  PROTHEROE
