                     <interp inst="t18311020-98-person749" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was on duty, and the prisoner was delivered to me.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was coming along St. Paul's church-yard, and kicked against the handkerchief; I took it up, and put it into my pocket - the gentleman asked me if I had picked his pocket; I said No, I had picked up a handkerchief - he opened my coat, and took it from my inside, not my breast-pocket.</p>
